<el-select :disabled="disabled" :value="valueTitle" @clear="clearHandle" clearable placeholder="故障类型">
    <el-option :label="valueTitle" :value="valueTitle">
        <el-tree
            :accordion="accordion"
            :data="options"
            :default-expanded-keys="defaultExpandedKey"
            :expand-on-click-node="false"
            :node-key="props.value"
            :props="props"
            @node-click="handleNodeClick"
            default-expand-all
            id="tree-option"
            ref="selectTree"
        ></el-tree>
    </el-option>
</el-select>
